sub_title: Private Lead at Founded in Groningen
summary: As a Private Lead at Founded in Groningen, I help local entrepreneurs and startups connect with investors, mentors, and resources to grow their businesses. I also lead the MXT Conference, a yearly event that brings together experts and innovators in the fields of marketing, experience, and technology. In addition, I serve as a Board Member at Yes! Digital, a community for startup founders. I am also the Founder of Zoinks, a creative agency that specializes in content marketing, branding, and a Podcaster who shares insights and stories about the digital world.
